---
// How It Works Section
// 3-step process explaining the NooLife journey
---

<section
  class="py-16 md:py-24 px-4"
  style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-rich-earth) 0%, var(--color-dark) 100%);"
>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h2
      class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-12 text-center"
      style="color: var(--color-alabaster);"
    >
      How It Works
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div
        class="p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-[rgba(241,237,233,0.08)] hover:border-[rgba(0,208,156,0.15)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
        style="background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.82); backdrop-filter: blur(24px);"
      >
        <div
          class="w-15 h-15 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-extrabold mb-6 border-[3px]"
          style="background-color: var(--color-jade); color: var(--color-rich-earth); border-color: var(--color-mint); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0, 208, 156, 0.3);"
        >
          1
        </div>
        <h3
          class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 leading-snug"
          style="color: var(--color-alabaster);"
        >
          Face the Truth
        </h3>
        <p
          class="text-base leading-relaxed"
          style="color: var(--color-faded-khaki);"
        >
          Rate yourself honestly across 8 core habits. See the gap between who
          you are <span class="font-bold text-[#ff6b6b]">(31/100)</span> and who
          you could be <span class="font-bold" style="color: var(--color-jade);"
            >(87/100)</span
          >. That uncomfortable feeling? That's the wake-up call you need.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div
        class="p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-[rgba(241,237,233,0.08)] hover:border-[rgba(0,208,156,0.15)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
        style="background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.82); backdrop-filter: blur(24px);"
      >
        <div
          class="w-15 h-15 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-extrabold mb-6 border-[3px]"
          style="background-color: var(--color-jade); color: var(--color-rich-earth); border-color: var(--color-mint); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0, 208, 156, 0.3);"
        >
          2
        </div>
        <h3
          class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 leading-snug"
          style="color: var(--color-alabaster);"
        >
          Your 66-Day Program Begins
        </h3>
        <p
          class="text-base leading-relaxed"
          style="color: var(--color-faded-khaki);"
        >
          No generic advice. Your personalized program stacks habits based on
          behavioral science. Intensity increases gradually. You get stronger,
          the system gets harder. That's how winners are built.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div
        class="p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-[rgba(241,237,233,0.08)] hover:border-[rgba(0,208,156,0.15)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
        style="background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.82); backdrop-filter: blur(24px);"
      >
        <div
          class="w-15 h-15 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-extrabold mb-6 border-[3px]"
          style="background-color: var(--color-jade); color: var(--color-rich-earth); border-color: var(--color-mint); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0, 208, 156, 0.3);"
        >
          3
        </div>
        <h3
          class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 leading-snug"
          style="color: var(--color-alabaster);"
        >
          Track Your Climb
        </h3>
        <p
          class="text-base leading-relaxed"
          style="color: var(--color-faded-khaki);"
        >
          Every completed task raises your rating. Every day you show up, you
          separate yourself from average. Watch your 31 turn into an 87. Visual
          proof you're leveling up.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
